<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Sihanouk Arrives for Cambodian Roundtable Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sihanouk Arrives for Cambodian Roundtable Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2605111594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1041 GMT 26 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2605111594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- His Majesty King Norodom 
Sihanouk of Cambodia arrived here today by special plane to 
preside over a roundtable for peace and national reconciliation 
of Cambodia slated in Pyongyang. 
  Arriving to attend the roundtable meeting were also H.E. 
Prince Chea Sim, acting head of state and president of the 
National Assembly, H.R.H. Prince Norodom Ranariddh, first prime 
minister, H.E. Prince Hun Sen, second prime minister, and the 
suite from the Cambodian Government side, and H.E. Khieu 
Samphan, president of the the Democratic Cambodia side, and the 
suite. 
  They were met at the airport by Yi Chong-ok, vice president, 
Kim Yong-nam, vice premier and minister of foreign affairs, and 
officials concerned. 
  Officials of the Royal Embassy of Cambodia in Pyongyang and 
Qiao Zonghuai, Chinese ambassador to Korea, were present at the 
airport. 

</TEXT>

