  [Text] Seoul's Tongdaemun Police conducted a seize and 
search procedure today at the office of the National Alliance 
for the Country's Reunification [Pomminnyon] located on Chongno 
6-ka in Seoul. Police disclosed that they conducted a seize and 
search for relevant documents following the South side 
headquarters of Pomminnyon's violation of the National Security 
