  [Text] Pyongyang, May 26 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialists 
committed long-distance non-stop bombing exercises against the 
North by formations of overseas-based pursuit-assault planes and 
VTOL assault planes in the sky above Yongwol and Pyongchang 
areas of South Korea on May 23 and 24, according to military 
sources. 
  A P-3 anti-submarine plane based in Japan made a low and an 
ultra low flight in the sky above the East and West Seas of 
Korea on May 23. 
  On the 23rd and 24th, scores of armed helicopters and 
transport helicopters of the South Korean puppet army staged 
ground attack supporting and airlifting operation exercises in 
the sky above the areas adjacent to the demilitarized zone of 
the Military Demarcation Line in Paju and Yonchon of Kyonggi 
Province and Chorwon of South Korean Kangwon Province, and 
large-calibre artillery units of the puppet army fired more than 
