<H3> <TI>   ROK Reacts to New Russia-DPRK Logging Agreement </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ROK Reacts to New Russia-DPRK Logging Agreement </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2705022394 Seoul SEOUL SINMUN in Korean 26 May 94 p 1 </F>
