<F P=104>  Seoul SEOUL SINMUN </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Regarding the issue pertaining to new logging 
agreement reached between Russia and North Korea, a government 
official evaluated on 24 May that "the recent agreement 
stipulates the improved treatment of North Korean loggers. This 
is a stepped-up measure," and expressed that "however, the 
government will continue its efforts to further improve loggers' 
working conditions and their human rights." 

</TEXT>

