  [Text] London, April 29 (AFP) -- A British soldier was 
killed and two injured when their Land-Rover went over an 
anti-tank mine in central Bosnia Friday [29 April], the Ministry 
of Defence said. The incident occurred near Gornji Vakuf, a 
